		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />...what lidnariq said...<br /><br />I think you have to type something like...<br /><br />.import _rand, _srand<br /><br />And CA65 automatically knows what you're talking about... I'm away from my computer at the moment, so I can't test it. Maybe you also need to have an include. (?)<br /><br />And then later...jsr _rand will put a pseudorandom number in A [and X].

		

