		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />This worked for me...(no need to include anything)<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; &nbsp;.import&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;_rand<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;.import&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;_srand<br /><br />.segment&nbsp; &nbsp;&quot;CODE&quot;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;;you should first put a seed value in...<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;jsr _srand<br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp;jsr _rand ;then this generates a new random number</div>

		

