		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The linker would need to know where to find _rand. It's in the common lib, but you can just look at the code yourself if you like:<br /><a href="https://github.com/cc65/cc65/blob/master/libsrc/common/rand.s" class="postlink">https://github.com/cc65/cc65/blob/master/libsrc/common/rand.s</a><br /><br />Alternatively, I put a simple PRNG implementation on the wiki a while back because it kept coming up: <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Random_number_generator" class="postlink">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Random_number_generator</a>

		

